update_water_light
Disk World creator help
update_water_light

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
update_water_light -  This function updates the amount of light filtering down to this room from the rooms above it, if it is necessary to do so.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void update_water_light()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/water.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function updates the amount of light filtering down to this room from
the rooms above it, if it is necessary to do so.  It is called by
query_light in /std/room/water_inside and /std/room/water_outside.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
set_use_surface_light, set_light, query_water_surface_light, get_water_surface_light

.EP

